quests.desc: It's time to explore the amazing world of TextWorld! First of all, make an attempt to head north. And then, go east. With that done, make an effort to take a trip east. That done, attempt to go to the south. After that, make an attempt to take a trip south. And then, make an effort to venture east. And then, make an effort to head south. Then, make an effort to head west. Then, take a trip west. And then, retrieve the golf tee from the rack. That's it!

objective: Hey, thanks for coming over to the TextWorld today, there is something I need you to do for me. First of all, you could, like, try to move north. Then, take a trip east. With that accomplished, attempt to go to the east. And then, go to the south. And then, make an attempt to head south. Then, make an effort to take a trip east. After that, make an attempt to move south. After that, travel west. And then, venture west. Next, take the golf tee from the rack. Once that's all handled, you can stop!
